== 不对称脱羧烯丙化反应==
使用[[手性配体|手性配体]]的[[不对称合成|不对称]]卡罗尔重排也有发展。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Enantioselective Palladium-Catalyzed Decarboxylative Allylic Alkylations|author=Shu-Li You and Li-Xin Dai|journal=[[Angew._Chem._Int._Ed.|Angew. Chem. Int. Ed.]]|year=2006|volume=45|issue=32|pages=5246–5248|doi=10.1002/anie.200601889}}</ref> 首个不对称重排由 Burger 等在 2004 年报道，是以[[三(二亚苄基丙酮)二钯(0)|三(二亚苄基丙酮)二钯(0)]]和[[Trost配体|Trost配体]]催化：<ref name=Burger>{{cite journal en|title=Asymmetric Allylic Alkylation of Ketone Enolates: An Asymmetric Claisen Surrogate|author=Erin C. Burger and Jon A. Tunge|journal=[[Org._Lett.|Org. Lett.]]|year=2004|volume=6|issue=22|pages=4113–4115|doi=10.1021/ol048149t}}</ref>

[[File:AsymmetricCarrol2005.png|center]]

[[桑野良一|桑野良一]]等报道了[[萘酚|萘酚]]存在下的卡罗尔重排，反应''[[对映体过量百分数|ee]]''可达88%，但缺点是底物必须要含[[乙酰氨基|乙酰氨基]]基团。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Kuwano, R.; Ishida N.; Murakami, M.|title=Asymmetric Carroll rearrangement of allyl α-acetamido-β-ketocarboxylates catalysed by a chiral palladium complex|journal=[[Chemical_Communications|Chem. Commun.]]|year=2005|issue=31|pages=3951–3952|doi=10.1039/b505105c}}.</ref>

[[File:AsymmetricCarrolRearrangement.png|center]]

又如如下[[对映归一性|对映归一性]]合成：<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Deracemization of Quaternary Stereocenters by Pd-Catalyzed Enantioconvergent Decarboxylative Allylation of Racemic β-Ketoesters|author=Justin T. Mohr, Douglas C. Behenna, Andrew M. Harned, and Brian M. Stoltz|journal=[[Angew._Chem._Int._Ed.|Angew. Chem. Int. Ed.]]|year=2005|volume=44|issue=42|pages=6924–6927|doi=10.1002/anie.200502018}}</ref>

